---
/**
 * Preview: Streaming AI chat
 * Shows a conversation streaming through Arlopass
 */
import PreviewPanel from "../ui/PreviewPanel.astro";
---

<PreviewPanel>
  <div
    data-step="0"
    class="flex items-center gap-2 pb-1 border-b border-[var(--ap-border)]"
  >
    <img
      src="/ArlopassIcon.svg"
      alt=""
      width="16"
      height="16"
      aria-hidden="true"
    />
    <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-[var(--ap-text-primary)]"
      >code-editor.dev</span
    >
    <span class="text-[10px] text-[var(--ap-text-tertiary)] ml-auto"
      >via Claude</span
    >
  </div>

  <div data-step="1" class="flex gap-2 items-start">
    <div
      class="w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-[var(--ap-bg-surface)] border border-[var(--ap-border)] flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 mt-0.5"
    >
      <svg
        width="10"
        height="10"
        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
        fill="none"
        stroke="var(--ap-text-tertiary)"
        stroke-width="2"
        stroke-linecap="round"
        stroke-linejoin="round"
        ><path d="M20 21v-2a4 4 0 00-4-4H8a4 4 0 00-4 4v2"></path><circle
          cx="12"
          cy="7"
          r="4"></circle></svg
      >
    </div>
    <div
      class="bg-[var(--ap-bg-surface)] border border-[var(--ap-border)] rounded-lg px-3 py-2 text-xs text-[var(--ap-text-body)] leading-relaxed"
    >
      Explain how async iterators work in TypeScript.
    </div>
  </div>

  <div data-step="2" class="flex gap-2 items-start">
    <div
      class="w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-brand-subtle flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 mt-0.5"
    >
      <img
        src="https://unpkg.com/@lobehub/icons-static-svg@latest/icons/claude.svg"
        alt=""
        width="11"
        height="11"
        class="provider-icon-sm"
      />
    </div>
    <div
      class="bg-brand-subtle border border-brand/10 rounded-lg px-3 py-2 text-xs text-[var(--ap-text-body)] leading-relaxed"
    >
      An async iterator implements the <code class="text-brand text-[11px]"
        >Symbol.asyncIterator</code
      > protocol, letting you use <code class="text-brand text-[11px]"
        >for await...of</code
      > loops to…
    </div>
  </div>

  <div data-step="3" class="flex items-center gap-2 pt-1">
    <div class="flex gap-0.5">
      <span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-brand animate-pulse"></span>
      <span
        class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-brand animate-pulse [animation-delay:150ms]"
      ></span>
      <span
        class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-brand animate-pulse [animation-delay:300ms]"
      ></span>
    </div>
    <span class="text-[10px] text-[var(--ap-text-tertiary)]"
      >Streaming via Arlopass · keys on your machine</span
    >
  </div>
</PreviewPanel>

<style>
  .provider-icon-sm {
    filter: brightness(0) invert(0.3);
  }
</style>
